# Empty

`TxEmpty` is the compact convenience wrapper for common empty panels. It renders `TxEmptyState` with `variant="empty"`, `surface="card"`, `layout="vertical"`, and a small/medium size controlled by `compact`.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/empty/src/TxEmpty.vue`, `types.ts`, and `empty.test.ts`.

## Basic Usage

### Empty
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="EmptyEmptyDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxEmpty title="No matching results" description="Adjust filters or clear the search keyword." icon-class="i-carbon-search" compact />
  </template>
---
:::

## With Actions

### Empty (action)
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="EmptyEmptyActionDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxEmpty title="No items yet" description="Create the first item to start managing this list.">
      <template #action>
        <TxButton type="primary">New item</TxButton>
      </template>
    </TxEmpty>
  </template>
---
:::

## Interaction Contract

- Always renders the wrapped `TxEmptyState` with `variant="empty"`, `surface="card"`, and `layout="vertical"`.
- `compact=false` maps to `size="medium"`; `compact=true` maps to `size="small"`.
- `iconClass` is forwarded as the wrapped empty-state `icon` prop.
- Slots are intentionally simpler than `TxEmptyState`: `action` is singular and replaces the wrapped `actions` slot.
- No events are emitted by `TxEmpty`; action behavior belongs to the slotted control.

## API

### Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| `title` | `string` | `'Nothing here'` | Primary empty-state message. |
| `description` | `string` | `''` | Supporting text shown below the title. |
| `iconClass` | `string` | `'i-carbon-incomplete'` | Icon class forwarded to the wrapped `TxEmptyState`. |
| `compact` | `boolean` | `false` | Uses the small empty-state size for dense panels. |

### Events

`TxEmpty` does not emit component events. Place click handlers on controls rendered inside the `action` slot.

## Slots

| Slot | Props | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| `icon` | - | Replaces the icon rendered by `iconClass`. |
| `title` | - | Replaces the title prop content. |
| `description` | - | Replaces the description prop content. |
| `action` | - | Replaces the wrapped `TxEmptyState` actions area. |

## Best Practices

- Use `TxEmpty` for compact list, search, or panel placeholders where the card surface is desirable.
- Use the more explicit `TxNoData`, `TxNoSelection`, `TxOfflineState`, or `TxPermissionState` when the empty cause has product meaning.
- Keep `compact` for dense regions such as sidebars and table interiors.
- Put clickable behavior inside the `action` slot; `TxEmpty` does not proxy action events.

